verbose_text: During the daytime, the transcription factors circadian locomotor output cycles kaput (CLOCK) and brain and muscle aryl hydrocarbon receptor nuclear translocator like 1 (BMAL1) heterodimerize and bind to E-box promoter elements to drive the gene expression of Period (Per1-3) and Cryptochrome (Cry1/2).
